  "text": "# REGULATORY & SAFETY  \n**Q: Is FirstUK Bank regulated?**\nA: Yes, by the FCA (Financial Conduct Authority) and PRA (Prudential Regulation Authority).  \n**Q: What if FirstUK Bank fails?**\nA: Your deposits (up to £85,000) are protected by FSCS.  \n**Q: How can I verify FirstUK is real?**\nA: Check FCA register at www.register.fca.org.uk (search \"FirstUK Bank\").  \n**Q: What if I have a data breach concern?**\nA: Contact our Data Protection Officer: dpo@firstuk.bank  \n---",
